{"tid":307853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新加坡房價破天荒連跌15季","createTime":"2017-07-03T16:16:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-04T01:42:41.000Z","uid":37554,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7503c798fcfcacfff2c04f120b3acc9096decbda","tid":307853,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T16:16:17.000Z","msg":"據新加坡市區重建局今天發布的數據，第2季新加坡房價下跌0.3%，為破天荒連續第15季走跌，如今住房價格已自2013年9月高峰下滑12%。<br />\n新加坡房屋銷售也已降至2013年峰值的一半。新加坡政府在今年3月小幅鬆綁部分抑制房價措施，但大部分的降溫措施仍繼續實施。<br />\n<br />\n新加坡央行上月底表示，房市抑制措施鬆綁的時間未到，政府3月做部分調整，不意味當局準備解除打房措施。<br />\n房價連15季走跌，為新加坡1975年開始記錄來最長跌勢。"},{"pid":"b801bca69b91ccceacfe16f44f531e7a0d7fd19d","tid":307853,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T16:16:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170703/420_41a3cdec00e764cd7a823de2a14e6807.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170703%2F420_41a3cdec00e764cd7a823de2a14e6807.jpg&h=804106d1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"45cb398f4095ea81d1fe2b51f27c2671c733c9a1","tid":307853,"uid":62506,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T16:29:30.000Z","msg":"如果唔係香港政府拓住個市，香港樓價一早要跌啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f59145f5b172f823ec59a87b912eb96a65de85fe","tid":307853,"uid":22858,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T16:40:59.000Z","msg":"同時新加坡經濟都收曬皮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f05e7bdacae74bb248c0dafe3dd092396ab06c8","tid":307853,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T17:04:51.000Z","msg":"大陸人快去果邊掃樓"},{"pid":"a4ca9e5ae4f41b4465717f1d364f80be970df637","tid":307853,"uid":56123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T17:09:17.000Z","msg":"13年9月到依家跌12%，除開一年跌3%，有序下跌"},{"pid":"84dbc64fa3cddcdb121a98d9f266656b0ca5040a","tid":307853,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dis